Program2 : rightAngleTriangle_left

START PROGRAM
	INCLUDE - Importing standard input/outp library
	PROTOTYPE FUNCTION - declare them before main [drawTriangle(char x)]
	MAIN -  Declaring main int function
		Declaring and Initializing char a = '*'
		Calling prototype function drawTriangle drawTriangle()
		
	FUNCTION: Function called passing a char parameter
		  Declaring variables to use i,j

		  FOR LOOP: Repeat until statement is reached  i<5
			    PRINT  a line after a loop is completed (\n)

			    FOR LOOP: Repeat until statement is reached  j<i
				      PRINT  j's number of starts ('*')
				      END FOR LOOP
		  END FOR LOOP
	RETURN
END PROGRAM
